Fractional decrease in kinetic energy of mass $m$
$$
\begin{aligned}
& =1-\left(\frac{m_2-m_1}{m_2+m_1}\right)^2=1-\left(\frac{2-1}{2+1}\right)^2 \\
& =1-\left(\frac{1}{3}\right)^2=1-\frac{1}{9}=\frac{8}{9}
\end{aligned}
$$
